### ############################################################
### AUTOMATION TESTS - PROACTIVE LOGIC
### ############################################################

@autoUserId = 2

### 30. [USER-AUTO-01] Role Change Automation (History + Notification)
### Expected: create an entry in /api/user-role-history and a notification titled "Rol actualizado".
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{autoUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "RESOURCE_MANAGEMENT"
}

###

### 31. [USER-AUTO-01-CHECK-A] Verify role change history for the user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/user-role-history?userId={{autoUserId}}&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 32. [USER-AUTO-01-CHECK-B] Verify ROLE_UPDATED notification for the affected user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications?type=ROLE_UPDATED&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{workerToken}}

###

### 33. [USER-AUTO-02] Fail-Fast: resend the current role (no-op)
### Expected: no new history entries or notifications are created.
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{autoUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "RESOURCE_MANAGEMENT"
}

###

### 34. [USER-AUTO-02-CHECK-A] Confirm history does not increase from baseline
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/user-role-history?userId={{autoUserId}}&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 35. [USER-AUTO-02-CHECK-B] Confirm ROLE_UPDATED does not increase from baseline
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications?type=ROLE_UPDATED&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{workerToken}}

###

### 36. [USER-AUTO-RESET] Restore original role to avoid affecting other tests
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{autoUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "WORKER"
}

###
